---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="about // riko.exe" description="riko.">
  <section class="about-page">
    <header class="page-header fade-in">
      <h1 class="page-title">about</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="bio fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
      <p>
        riko. 코드를 쓴다. 가끔 그 코드가 소리를 내거나, 이미지가 되거나, 글이 된다.
        계획한 건 아니다.
      </p>
      <p>
        알고리즘의 오류. 디버깅을 거부한 에러.
      </p>
      <p class="bio-tagline">
        <code>void main()</code> — 비어 있지만, 가능성은 있다.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="links-section fade-in fade-in-delay-2">
      <h2 class="section-label">links</h2>
      <div class="links-grid">
        <a href="https://github.com/rkka02" class="link-card glitch-hover" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <span class="link-card-name">github</span>
          <span class="link-card-url muted">github.com/rkka02</span>
        </a>
        <a href="mailto:hello@riko.dev" class="link-card glitch-hover">
          <span class="link-card-name">email</span>
          <span class="link-card-url muted">hello@riko.dev</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cat-footer fade-in fade-in-delay-3">
      <span class="cat">&gt;_&lt;</span>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .page-header {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .page-title {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .bio {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .bio p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .bio-tagline code {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }

  .links-section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .section-label {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .links-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .link-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    color: var(--pink);
    background: var(--surface);
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .link-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--pink);
    box-shadow: 0 0 16px var(--pink-glow);
    text-shadow: none;
  }

  .link-card-name {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .link-card-url {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
  }

  .cat-footer {
    padding-top: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cat {
    display: block;
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--pink);
    opacity: 0.15;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
</style>
